cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with detecting spam campaigns on Twitter, which involves analyzing a large amount of social network data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for spam detection, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper involves network analysis, which falls under cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
